quests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;SPOP: 149253.73 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;LPUSH (needed to benchmark LRANGE): 148588.42 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;LRANGE_100 (first 100 elements): 58411.21 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;LRANGE_300 (first 300 elements): 21195.42 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;LRANGE_500 (first 450 elements): 14539.11 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;LRANGE_600 (first 600 elements): 10504.20 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;MSET (10 keys): 93283.58 requests per second&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
